blogs.subTitle: It was Saturday night hanging around
blogs.text: It was Saturday night hanging around to solve the issue of “ReferenceError: legacyLib is not defined” in my React+Typescript app. I was sure that this error was about my “legacyLib.js” lib file, which included thousands of lines of code coded as IIFE, which wasn’t bundled by webpack by default.
